(1939, 321, '_elementor_data', '[{"id":"43e40e4","elType":"section","settings":{"stretch_section":"section-stretched","background_background":"classic","background_image":{"url":"http:\\/\\/178.62.60.96\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2018\\/11\\/rawpixel-604748-unsplash.jpg","id":257},"background_position":"center center","background_repeat":"no-repeat","background_size":"cover","background_overlay_background":"classic","background_overlay_color":"#ffffff","padding":{"unit":"px","top":"20","right":"0","bottom":"20","left":"0","isLinked":false}},"elements":[{"id":"93dadbd","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":100,"content_position":"center","space_between_widgets":20,"padding":{"unit":"px","top":"10","right":"0","bottom":"10","left":"0","isLinked":false}},"elements":[{"id":"f48dd2f","elType":"widget","settings":{"space":{"unit":"px","size":10}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"spacer"},{"id":"51d4f14","elType":"widget","settings":{"title":"A propos","align":"center"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"heading"},{"id":"e114aa8","elType":"widget","settings":{"editor":"<p>Tout ce qu\'il faut savoir sur la marque !<\\/p>","align":"center"},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false},{"id":"5e2f3a7","elType":"section","settings":[],"elements":[{"id":"addfcd0","elType":"column","settings":{"_column_size":100},"elements":[{"id":"91eb9d6","elType":"widget","settings":{"editor":"<h2>Bonjour, nous sommes Titime !<\\/h2><p>Tamia et Julia fondent Titime en 2006 autour d\\u2019une tasse de th\\u00e9. Elles imaginent un concept permettant de faire d\\u00e9couvrir des th\\u00e9s d\\u2019excellence et de nouvelles saveurs au travers d\\u2019un coffret au <strong>design exclusif<\\/strong>. D\\u00e9nicheuses de nouvelles saveurs, elles con\\u00e7oivent plusieurs <strong>Th\\u00e9 de luxe<\\/strong>: Th\\u00e9s noirs, blanc, aux l\\u00e9gumes,, d\\u00e9tox, mais aussi infusions !<\\/p><h2>\\u00ab Notre credo ? R\\u00e9inventer le tea time, faire d\\u00e9couvrir le th\\u00e9 comme une boisson de luxe, rare. \\u00bb<\\/h2><div class=\\"abouthead--desc\\"><div class=\\"about--markup markup\\"><p>Un coup de c\\u0153ur ? Th\\u00e9, Th\\u00e9 Box, infusion, douceurs, th\\u00e9 forts en go\\u00fbts\\u2026 On y retrouve tout ce qui agr\\u00e9mente joyeusement le tea time. A offrir, \\u00e0 s\\u2019offrir et \\u00e0 partager !<\\/p><p>Au fil des ann\\u00e9es, tasse apr\\u00e8s tasse, Tamia &amp; Julia se sont prises au jeu de cr\\u00e9er leurs propres m\\u00e9langes. A chaque moment correspond un th\\u00e9 !<\\/p><h1 class=\\"aboutteam--title\\">L\'\\u00e9quipe<\\/h1><div class=\\"aboutteam--markup markup\\"><p>Titime, c\\u2019est une \\u00e9quipe de passionn\\u00e9s, de curieux, f\\u00e9rus de nouvelles saveurs, des hommes et des femmes (mais surtout des femmes) qui partagent leurs id\\u00e9es entre deux tasses de th\\u00e9.<br \\/>Notre objectif ? Surprendre nos clients et combler leurs papilles, avec des th\\u00e9s d\\u2019excellence et des gourmandises exquises. Le tout avec une bonne dose de cr\\u00e9ativit\\u00e9 !<\\/p><\\/div><\\/div><\\/div>","_padding":{"unit":"px","top":"50","right":"0","bottom":"50","left":"0","isLinked":false}},"elements":[],"widgetType":"text-editor"}],"isInner":false}],"isInner":false}]'),
